Hey Jarhead, Webfoot, Mud-wrestling, Commie Killer:<br><br>
Go easy on the medals (I have several sacks full of them!)  Do you think it was easy for me to fly over your position and drop deodorant and comic books?  <br>
While you were down there beating up on little guys half your size... I was braving the elements... breaking the surley bonds of the earth... cheating gravity... taking chances on getting hopelessy lost!<br>
Do you have any idea how much fear I experienced... gut wrenching FEAR...realizing that I might be late in getting back to see the USO shows... and getting a bad seat.  Have some compassion... Mortar Magnet... Punji Stake face... Camouflage Panties!<br><br>
Your Idol, Mustang Two Four
